?!

PS I can no longer reproduce (but it was reliably failing for me earlier, both before and after your message pointing out that it did exist)
Getting back to the main point, I golfed my proof a little more and I can't see how to make it shorter with `zmodCyclicMulEquiv`; can you?
I didn't have anything precise in mind, it only looks like a reasonable strategy. It's not very important.
